properties.name: mapDescription
properties.value:
Suitable for up to 300 users.

Counting with several meeting zones spread out throughout the map, four main big rooms for your conferences and a garden for your chillout sessions.
This is the map you are looking for when you have a populated event and need everyone to be able to meet in a simple yet efficient way.
